<body >
<br>
<b>Attn:</b> Administrator/Trustee                                                                                                    
<br><br>

Dear Sir / Madam, 
<br><br>

In an effort to keep our records current, we are kindly requesting an update for the above-noted Insolvency filed with your office. According to our records we have not received an expected dividend for the below mentioned account(s):

<br><br>

{!AccountList}

</br>

Please advise if the Insolvency is:

<br><br>

Ongoing
<ul class="ul-style">
<li class="li-style">Has our claim been received and admitted? </li>
<li class="li-style">Have any dividends been issued / when can we expect dividends? </li>
</ul>

<br>
Annulled
<ul class="ul-style">
<li class="li-style">Date of annulment and Trustee discharge?  </li>
<li class="li-style">Has a subsequent bankruptcy been filed? If yes, please provide new Estate information </li>
</ul>
<br>

Discharged
<ul class="ul-style">
<li class="li-style">Date of full performance? </li>
<li class="li-style">Were any dividends issued for the account(s) listed?  </li>
</ul>
<br>

Any other information that you may be able to provide would be greatly appreciated. 
<br><br>
Thank you in advance for your assistance. 
<br><br><br>
Sincerely  
<br><br><br>

Canaccede International Management Ltd. 
<br>

Insolvency Department
